INSTRUCTIONS
------------
- Do NOT change the header file "alpha_T.h". It works fine!

- To run the code all you have to do is execute the "run.C" macro in
  ROOT, as following:

|myTerm> root -l
root[ ] .x run.C

- The list of files to be run are given by the means of a TChain in
  the "run.C" macro.